sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as ML Pipeline Controller<br/>(Data Science Pipelines)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as Database<br/>(MySQL 3306 / PostgreSQL 5432)
    participant UI as Pipeline UI<br/>(Frontend)

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording
    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution (atomic upsert)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Note right of DSP: Records pipeline run,<br/>artifacts, events, contexts
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata entities<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol, Optional SSL
    Note right of MLMD: Username/password auth
    DB-->>MLMD: SQL Result (rows affected)
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts (batch)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT artifacts + properties
    DB-->>MLMD: SQL Result
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactsResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutEvents (link artifacts to executions)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT events (INPUT/OUTPUT)
    DB-->>MLMD: SQL Result
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutEventsResponse

    Note over UI,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query
    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Note right of UI: Graph traversal with<br/>configurable hops & direction
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with JOIN traversal<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage graph rows
    MLMD-->>UI: LineageSubgraph<br/>(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)

    UI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    Note right of UI: Filter via ListOperationOptions<br/>(ZetaSQL-parsed filter_query)
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with filter predicates
    DB-->>MLMD: Filtered artifact rows
    MLMD-->>UI: GetArtifactsByContextResponse
